title: Independent candidate Raja Khuram Shehzad Nawaz wins NA-48 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Raja Khuram Shehzad Nawaz has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-48 Islamabad-III by securing 69,699 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Syed Muhammad Ali Bukhari, who bagged 59,851 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 61.10 percent.
